《'''神鬼尖兵'''》（{{lang-en|''The Boondock Saints''}}）是一部1999年美國[[犯罪片|犯罪片]]，由[[特洛伊·達菲|-{特洛伊}-·達菲]]執導和編劇，[[威廉·達佛|威廉·達佛]]、[[西恩·派翠克·福納瑞|西恩·派翠克·福納瑞]]、[[諾曼·李杜斯|諾曼·李杜斯]]、[[大衛·德拉·洛克|大衛·德拉·洛克]]和[[比利·康諾利|比利·康諾利]]主演。故事敘述一對[[愛爾蘭裔美國人|愛爾蘭裔美國]]雙胞胎麥克曼奴兄弟（片中未表明長幼順序）受到了上帝的「指示」，動用私刑剷除[[俄羅斯黑手黨|俄羅斯黑手黨]]，後來和朋友「滑稽小子」一同決心將[[波士頓|波士頓]]的犯罪與邪惡清除，而[[联邦调查局|FBI]]特工保羅也同時在追擊著他們。

達菲表示劇本是來自個人住在[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]的經驗<ref name="filmvault">{{cite news | last = Finch | first = Amy | url = http://www.filmvault.com/filmvault/boston/b/boondocksaints1.html | title = Boondock Saints | work = filmvault.com | date = 1998-11-02 | accessdate = 2009-03-30 | archive-date = 2018-09-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180929091241/http://www.filmvault.com/filmvault/boston/b/boondocksaints1.html | dead-url = no }} (Republished from ''[[The_Phoenix_(newspaper)|Boston Phoenix]]''.)</ref>。最初認為是好萊塢最炙手可熱的劇本之一，但電影的製作卻陷入難產，後來電影終於1999年1月22日在美國上映。但因僅在限定地區的五間戲院放映一週，所以獲得了相當慘澹的票房；最後加上DVD在國內的銷售，最終票房約5000萬美元<ref name=nytwww />，且之後獲得了[[邪典電影|邪典電影]]的地位<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.detroitbuzz.com/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=585&Itemid=95 | title = Boondock Saints, the infamous Cult Classic | accessdate = 2006-12-14 | work = Detroitbuzz.com Cult Corner | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20061102005411/http://detroitbuzz.com/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=585&Itemid=95 | archive-date = 2006-11-02 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref name = RE >{{cite news | url = http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20041118/REVIEWS/41116007/1023 | title = Overnight | accessdate = 2006-12-14 | work = [[Roger_Ebert|Roger Ebert]] review | archive-date = 2012-10-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121011051239/http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20041118%2FREVIEWS%2F41116007%2F1023 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.dvdfuture.com/review.php?id=838 DVDfutue.com | title = DVD Review - Boondock Saints unrated edition | accessdate = 2006-11-28 | work = DVDfuture.com | archive-date = 2018-10-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181005053706/http://www.dvdfuture.com/review.php?id=838 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

