== 發行 ==
=== 評價 ===
於[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於25位專業影評人持有20％的新鮮度，平均得分4.2／10；該網站共識：「一部幼稚、醜陋的電影，這代表了最糟的導演塔倫提諾之趨勢」，雖然象徵著差評，但觀眾卻給予了91％的分數<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/boondock_saints| title = The Boondock Saints Movie Reviews, Pictures| publisher = Rottentomatoes.com| accessdate = 2011-04-22| archive-date = 2021-03-18| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210318095611/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/boondock_saints| dead-url = no}}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上根據279條評論，得分44（滿分100），評價好壞參雜。

=== 票房 ===
最初僅在限定地區的五間戲院放映一週，因此僅有3萬0471美元的淒慘票房<ref name=nytwww>{{cite news| url = http://www.nytimes.com/2009/10/18/movies/18ande.html| title = Back to the Boondocks, Defiantly| accessdate = 2009-10-16| work = The New York Times| first = John| last = Anderson| date = 2009-10-18| archive-date = 2020-11-12| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112024944/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/10/18/movies/18ande.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>。後來發行DVD時以粉絲的支持使得最終票房約5000萬美元<ref name=nytwww />。

